show.description: Controlled by Viper, a crime organization, with a lethal chip planted in her brain, Agent Bertha goes to steal a legendary diamond ring at the wedding of Edward, the richest man in the nation. She surprisingly walks in on Wilde, Edward's best friend, making out with Cynthia, the bride. Just when she think she's busted by Edward, who comes in right after her, Edward gets furious at the adultery and declares he will marry Bertha instead...
